literal

public static FieldBasedTupleMatcher literal(com.streambase.sb.Tuple t)
create a FieldBasedTupleMatcher that will match the Tuple exactly.

NOTE: This method will attempt to do the correct thing, returning RatioTestDoubleValueMatcher for doubles and properly trawling the hierarchy of the provided Tuple to create a suitably composed FieldBasedTupleMatcher

emptyFieldMatcher

public static FieldBasedTupleMatcher emptyFieldMatcher()
create a FieldBasedTupleMatcher that will match any Tuple.

This is usually used as a base for more complicated matchers.
